name: auth-source-search
demo_src:
(let ((tmpfile (make-temp-file "elisp-demos-authinfo-")))
(write-region
(concat "machine foo.com login user1 password pass1" " "
"machine bar.com login user2 password pass2" " "
"machine baz.com login user3 password pass2" " ")
nil tmpfile)
(unwind-protect
(let ((auth-source-do-cache nil)
(auth-sources (list tmpfile)))
(when-let ((plist (car (auth-source-search :host "bar.com" :max 1)))
(user (plist-get plist :user))
(pass (funcall (plist-get plist :secret))))
(list user pass)))
(delete-file tmpfile)))

name: iter-do

(iter-defun foo-number-sequence (start)
(while t
(iter-yield start)
(setq start (1+ start))))

(catch 'break
(let ((count 0) result)
(iter-do (n (foo-number-sequence 1))
(if (< count 10)
(push n result)
(throw 'break (nreverse result)))
(setq count (1+ count)))))

name: xmlgen
demo_src:
((lambda (string)
"Prettify HTML in STRING."
(with-temp-buffer
(insert string)
(html-mode)
(sgml-pretty-print (point-min) (point-max))
(buffer-string)))
(xmlgen '(html
(head
(title "Example Domain")
(meta :charset "utf-8"))
(body
(h1 "Example Domain")
(p "This domain...")
(p (a :href "http://www.iana.org/domains/example" "More information..."))))))
